<title>UK: Clarke says UK public finances better expectations.</title>
<headline>Clarke says UK public finances better expectations.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-04-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>Britain's Chancellor of the Exchequer Kenneth Clarke said on Friday that public finances were doing &quot;rather better than expected&quot;.</p>
